snippet.title: Storybook of Tactics - rogue-lite auto battler with deck building elements
snippet.description:
Wishlist and try it on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2511340/Storybook_of_Tactics/

Storybook of Tactics is a rogue-lite auto battler with deck building elements. Survive all the story chapters, upgrade unit cards, and experiment with dozens of builds while acquiring game-changing powers and powerful items.

Legendary Epic Heroic | Heroic by Alex-Productions |
https://youtu.be/Wfs69Jc1qYM?si=24w1-uwCWFy9YmJl
Music promoted by http://onsound.eu/

Particle Stock Videos by Vecteezy https://www.vecteezy.com/
